# Generated artifacts — excluded from authored-source metrics, diffs, and
# GitHub-linguist language stats (fix-22).
#
# vmlinux.h is a 168K-line BTF dump emitted by `bpftool btf dump file
# /sys/kernel/btf/vmlinux format c` — by far the largest file in the tree and
# entirely machine-generated.  Without these attributes it inflates the C/
# header LOC breakdown by ~38% over the hand-written headers and dumps the
# whole blob into every `git diff` / `git blame` that touches it.
#   linguist-generated  → drop from language stats AND collapse in PR diffs
#   linguist-vendored   → also exclude from "your code" surfaces
#   -diff               → never emit a textual diff for it
include/crucible/perf/bpf/vmlinux.h linguist-generated=true linguist-vendored=true -diff
